verbose_text: Immunostaining with an anti-rEtMIC2 antibody showed that the EtMIC2 protein mainly localized in the anterior region and membrane of sporozoites, in the cytoplasm of first- and second generation merozoites, and was strongly expressed during first-stage schizogony.
